<%- include('partials/head', { title: 'How it works' }) %>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<div class="page">
<section class="page-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="page-header a-fade-up">
      <div class="section-tag">How it works</div>
      <h2>Four steps. No dashboards to maintain, no accounts to link.</h2>
      <p>You hand us the raw material — renewal emails, invoices, PDFs, screenshots. We extract the details, form an opinion, and deliver it in a single email each week. No portal to log into, no app to install.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="steps a-fade-up steps-a">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-index">01</div>
        <h3>Forward or upload</h3>
        <div class="step-desc">Forward a renewal email to your perch. address, or drag a PDF, contract, or screenshot into the upload panel. Two seconds, done.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-index">02</div>
        <h3>AI extracts it</h3>
        <div class="step-desc">Provider, category, amount, renewal date, and cancellation notice period — pulled out automatically. No dropdowns, no tags, no manual entry.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-index">03</div>
        <h3>Get a verdict</h3>
        <div class="step-desc">Renew, cancel, or renegotiate — with the reasoning shown plainly. Not a vague nudge. A clear opinion you can act on or ignore in under a minute.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-index">04</div>
        <h3>Monday digest</h3>
        <div class="step-desc">One email, once a week: exactly what needs attention, ranked by deadline and cost. Nothing else from us in your inbox. No notifications, no spam.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="page-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="page-header a-fade-up">
      <div class="section-tag">Why it works</div>
      <h2>Low effort, high signal, zero noise.</h2>
      <p>The products that try to "manage all your finances" end up ignored because they demand too much setup and attention. perch. inverts that — minimal input, maximal clarity, then it gets out of your way.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="not-grid a-fade-up" style="margin-top:0;">
      <div class="not-card" style="border-color:var(--accent-line);">
        <div style="color:var(--accent);font-size:24px;margin-bottom:14px;">✓</div>
        <h3>Email-only workflow</h3>
        <p>Everything happens through email. Forward something and forget about it. The digest arrives Monday morning — no app, no login, no notification badge.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="not-card" style="border-color:var(--accent-line);">
        <div style="color:var(--accent);font-size:24px;margin-bottom:14px;">✓</div>
        <h3>Opinionated by design</h3>
        <p>We don't present raw data and ask you to decide. Every item comes with a recommendation based on the numbers, the context, and what we see across all perch. users.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="not-card" style="border-color:var(--accent-line);">
        <div style="color:var(--accent);font-size:24px;margin-bottom:14px;">✓</div>
        <h3>Privacy as default</h3>
        <p>No accounts linked. No transaction history ingested. You control what you send, and you can delete any item — or your entire account — at any time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</div>

<section class="page-section not-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="page-header a-fade-up">
      <div class="section-tag">The Monday digest</div>
      <h2>What lands in your inbox. Nothing else.</h2>
      <p>One email, Monday morning. Three sections: what needs attention, what's coming up, what's fine. You can read it in under 90 seconds and close it until next week.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="digest-mockup a-fade-up">
      <div class="digest-header">
        <div class="digest-from">
          <div class="digest-avatar">P</div>
          <div>
            <div class="digest-name">perch. digest</div>
            <div class="digest-addr">digest@perch.app</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="digest-to">to you <span class="digest-arrow">▼</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="digest-subject">Your perch. digest — 3 items need attention this week</div>
      <div class="digest-body">
        <div class="digest-intro">Good morning. Here's what's changed since last Monday.</div>

        <div class="digest-section">
          <div class="digest-sectitle"><span class="digest-dot urgent"></span> Needs action this week</div>
          <div class="digest-item">
            <div class="digest-verdict urgent">Renegotiate</div>
            <div class="digest-info">
              <div class="digest-provider">Direct Line — Home Insurance</div>
              <div class="digest-meta">£487.20/yr · renews 19 Aug · <span class="digest-up">up 26%</span> from last year</div>
            </div>
            <div class="digest-deadline">13 days</div>
          </div>
          <div class="digest-item">
            <div class="digest-verdict cancel">Cancel</div>
            <div class="digest-info">
              <div class="digest-provider">Adobe Creative Cloud</div>
              <div class="digest-meta">£59.99/mo · renews 3 Sep · <span class="digest-warn">unused 4 months</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="digest-deadline">28 days</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="digest-section">
          <div class="digest-sectitle"><span class="digest-dot coming"></span> Coming up</div>
          <div class="digest-item">
            <div class="digest-verdict monitor">Renew</div>
            <div class="digest-info">
              <div class="digest-provider">Virgin Media — Broadband</div>
              <div class="digest-meta">£38.00/mo · renews 17 Oct · price unchanged</div>
            </div>
            <div class="digest-deadline">72 days</div>
          </div>
          <div class="digest-item">
            <div class="digest-verdict monitor">Monitor</div>
            <div class="digest-info">
              <div class="digest-provider">AA — Breakdown Cover</div>
              <div class="digest-meta">£156.00/yr · renews 2 Nov · notice period 28 days</div>
            </div>
            <div class="digest-deadline">88 days</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="digest-footer-line">Extracted from 14 documents · Next digest Mon 17 Jul</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
